name: Dr.Plague
description:
The mask made the plague doctors look like birds. ...

They believed the plague was spread by bad air. Any air that had an unpleasant odor was suspect. For that reason, the doctors put herbs and flowers in the beak of their masks.

-
I always liked half of people's faces, it seemed mysterious to me. And finally I decided to portray this interest in the form of my own point of view... 

I hope it will be interesting for you too.



_
